oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Embree Iron Co. store
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Embree Iron Company Store. Embreeville, Tenn. "Amount of order $2500.00 July 23, 1906." In Washington County, TN. Shows people on porch of the store (man in suit by post, 3rd from left, identified as J.C. Love). Horse and loaded wagon at right.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Stores & shops; Carts & wagons; Horses;
